commit.message:
Completely refactor associative and commutative functionality

This approach uses associative flattening (e.g. `(op, 1, (op, 2, 3))` is
flattened to `(op, 1, 2, 3)`), which now makes nested associative operations
possible.
Add a non-relational groundedness ordering goal
